{
  "stem": "27340.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they-- they managed to stay at home for the time being.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Sacher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know his first name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, in Germany everything, especially children vis-a-vis adults, was always by, by the family name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was known as Herr Sacher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had a wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were pleasant people and they had two sons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were roughly of my brother's and my age.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we often played with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Early on, in the early days, we used to play in the garden and perhaps even on the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Later on, the thing became a little bit more dicey and we played either in our abode with the boys, or sometimes we went downstairs to their abode.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I suppose on reflection that was at the request of Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sacher, who possibly didn't want others to see that his boys were playing with Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that seemed to make some sense, anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father and grandfather then remained in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They obviously didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't leave the house during the Kristallnacht [GERMAN] operation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, if you like, in their own house, always worried that the Nazis may come back again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it's perhaps interesting to note that on the very first day, on the morning of all this activity, a lady who used to come-- non-Jews, who used to come and help in the house, was sort of a cleaner, if you like-- phoned up very early in the morning my mother and said, whatever you do, do not send the children to school today.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when my mother asked why, she said, well, just don't send them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then she hang up.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
